Introduction

Jay is a South Korean singer New Ways Company. He is the leader of the upcoming boy group ASC2NT, and a former member of the boy groups XING and DGNA, as well as its sub-unit Popsicle.

He made his acting debut beginning in 2009 with a supporting role in the movie Short! Short! Short!. He received his first main role in 2011 with the movie Themselves and also starred in the movie Confession as a supporting role in 2014.
